	<text_base_description>Nestled on a Serene and Tranquil Hollywood Hills Canyon Road, this fabulous Traditional Style home oozing with Character and Charm offers an Open Floor Plan with Vaulted Ceilings, Newer Kitchen with Breakfast Bar, Dining Area, Fireplace, Hardwood Floors and French Doors that open out to a lovely Rear Garden and Terraced Hillside View. This warm and welcoming Home boasts 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, a Den/4th Bedroom, and Laundry Room. An impressive Master Suite including a Gorgeous Bath  &amp;  Separate Office occupy the second floor, opening to a Spacious Private Wrap-Around Patio, the perfect setting for basking in the Peaceful Surroundings of Canyon Life! Other incredible attributes include: Electric Car Charger, Culligan Salt Water Softener, Retractable Awning off Master, Brand New Gate, Sonos/Speakers, Vaulted Ceilings, Skylights, Faux Grass, Tankless Water Heater, Storage Room, Security Cameras/Doorbell and 3 Private Parking Spaces! Freshly Painted! Wonderland Avenue Elementary School! </text_base_description>
